# 9. Errors We Faced

Now the interesting part.

---

## Error 1

Docker Desktop

Not Running.

Error

```text
error during connect
```

Root Cause

Docker Engine stopped.

Solution

Start Docker Desktop.

---

## Error 2

Frontend Build Failed

Remember

We accidentally wrote

```dockerfile
RUN RUN npm install
```

Docker output

```text
/bin/sh

RUN

not found
```

Root Cause

Typing mistake.

Solution

Removed extra RUN.

---

## Error 3

Backend Port

5000 already in use.

Error

```text
EADDRINUSE
```

Root Cause

PM2 already running backend.

Solution

Find process

```bash
sudo lsof -i :5000
```

Stop process.

---

## Error 4

Docker Cache

Sometimes

Old build reused.

Solution

```bash
docker compose build --no-cache
```

